轉，google map叫佢右轉</blockquote><br />\nGoogle hk垃圾到不能再垃圾"},{"pid":"d9b592da1bc70e3470c76ad98c8db9e4895e4f63","tid":93214,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:03:43.000Z","msg":"明明大河道可以直去，google map叫你兜個大圈再响只可以直去既沙咀道夾硬右轉去大河道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/140134_c39c4085b17b103180d2ded43b62e444.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F140134_c39c4085b17b103180d2ded43b62e444.jpg&h=d8a12fee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac018a7a24e57eb36aa5d656cc65e931dd579341","tid":93214,"uid":27575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:04:46.000Z","msg":"spotify<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5448654a4f7034ce47c020b0fbcebd7a7fb0421d","tid":93214,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:38:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e704b90b3126d00f6d17b4721288b8cdec8312cd","tid":93214,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:41:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高德<br />\n路況垃撚圾，但係分叉路同埋地面畫線最好用，會提你入線</blockquote><br />\n高德個路況如果有提供既話其實唔差<br />\n寫埋車龍有幾長同要塞幾耐，都算準<br />\n<br />\n同埋會預早同你講前面塞車，要唔要行條兜遠左但係冇塞車既替代路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6185082a3c3b1c6ac45ee8f8f3e0d3092d18c92e","tid":93214,"uid":24966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T12:59:29.000Z","msg":"Try waze"},{"pid":"e4af4f01420879bbb10e5473e5dd48f93380e4df","tid":93214,"uid":4032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T23:54:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明大河道可以直去，google map叫你兜個大圈再响只可以直去既沙咀道夾硬右轉去大河道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/140134_c39c4085b17b103180d2ded43b62e444.jpg\