"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69819680d9c8da0004b400075ba2aaf6f6ff9943","tid":93214,"uid":858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:47:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真渣車用呢d gps app唔會好食電咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 有車叉架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9301436aa52882e6f8baba85aa09c36b10723955","tid":93214,"uid":79355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:26:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Waze UX is pErfect<br />\n但係佢很需要大量用家，而且香港冇路面情況<br />\n十分可惜...</blockquote><br />\n無Lane guidance 都perfect?<br />\n<br />\nPs外國用"},{"pid":"c2fc4be1a918625015739a6ed721e93ca420a816","tid":93214,"uid":20602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:26:59.000Z","msg":"高德你地用高德導航定係高德地圖?"},{"pid":"56ceabd2f494e52e702a1e65842918e1c4806bb8","tid":93214,"uid":4006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:31:32.000Z","msg":"有冇咁多高德打手 痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d10b4625d02e8ead912f74d787e36d32d7bd98b","tid":93214,"uid":11284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:31:42.000Z","msg":"以前完全唔識路就用高德 Google導航遠程好伏<br />\n而家渣熟左去到附近用Google Map<br />\n沒再用高德"},{"pid":"f677091dbd8383c52637bd280081992fe28a79fb","tid":93214,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:04:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48470af26d4a168c90b223fb84ce0ed3d68ead05","tid":93214,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:07:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c69357051d9d83f5ea71577cda058235907f26fd","tid":93214,"uid":7291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:47:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高德自從加埋出口號碼之後就好好用，<br />\n除左係咁叫你u turn之外同埋有d唔比轉彎既路口叫你轉彎之外，<br />\nGoogle既行車線指引係做得無高德咁好，<br />\n高德個畫面會show晒前面地線係咩樣，叫你入邊條線，<br />\n特別係港島區地面d線畫到七彩，入唔到線就要兜大圈</blockquote><br />\n你講既野好中point<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n圖我覺得唔一定需要，但邊條lane一定要好清楚<br />\nGoogle而家係有show，但好多路都係錯，<br />\n例如明明四五條lane會變左得三條<br />\n<br />\n哩個都正正係我用高德一個好大既原因<br />\n<br />\n同埋感覺上收唔到gps既時候<br />\n雖然兩個app都唔準<br />\n但google 會彈黎彈去<br />\n但高德唔會 係「定」啲<br />\n<br />\n但高德無得打英文 搵地方無google咁勁<br />\n成日都要開google搵左 再係高德標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a257c2d8167ea9a58ef8e4458313be9348f792","tid":93214,"uid":7291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:49:05.000Z","msg":"同埋google map成條彌敦道都係可以u turn的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9105232d2e9daab6d8b68b168d8b1971030ff2d1","tid":93214,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:17:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講真渣車用呢d gps app唔會好食電咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 有車叉架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問得呢句證明佢冇揸過車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe656f53772a0e8384de0bee1756f6535162adb","tid":93214,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:28:17.000Z","msg":"香港交通情況<br />\n睇交通消息~"},{"pid":"47e8038a728ab140bcb361190c777af61716984d","tid":93214,"uid":78700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:32:46.000Z","msg":"HERE <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb837615a96b14370ec3028b7675365cc417c5bc","tid":93214,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T06:36:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>導航就Google同埋高德都有用<br />\n感覺高德好用D 起碼有圖話你知邊個出口出<br />\nGoogle淨係同你講幾多米出 有時好容易就過左</blockquote><br />\n痴線<br />\nGoogle寫埋出口號碼同埋名，齋睇電話唔睇路梗係唔識出<br />\n<br />\n地政署MyMapHK都好用<br />\n可以search哂成個area既鏢位同停車場"},{"pid":"f73bece1c